{"tid":494944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"芬蘭慶祝獨立建國百年 引世界「藍白」響應","createTime":"2017-12-10T08:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T08:48:45.000Z","uid":60545,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"37d4d385ba9ff01de8079d287580041b5433a8ff","tid":494944,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕歷經1917年12月6日的俄國革命後，芬蘭以獨立共和國的身分建國。直到今年芬蘭為慶祝建國100周年，在臉書以1個「芬蘭（Finland、芬蘭文：Suomi） 100」的活動號召，吸引世界各國紛紛響應，其中許多知名建築用芬蘭國旗的藍、白二色為光源，在夜晚中大放異彩。包括紐約的帝國大廈、里約的基督像、葡萄牙的貝倫塔（Bel&eacute;m Tower）、羅馬競技場等，其中芬蘭打亮1029公尺莎娜山（Saana Mountain），用藍、白光及北極光相互輝映下，整座山變得更加立體。<br />\n<br />\n除了各國用「藍白」響應外，也有用實際行動證明的國家，在羅馬競技場前合唱團高歌一曲，慶祝芬蘭100周年誕辰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2276664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2276664&d=K8wAcjet1HEbSDaO5PBrvZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9368a970\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2276664&h=a0e31b59\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2276664</a>"},{"pid":"099f81edef9564301680fe1a7d67837aee4e91b8","tid":494944,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T08:47:07.000Z","msg":"Sisu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9935eee68493c853fabdca614cd1d65c9ebc419c","tid":494944,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T08:48:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}